<a href="/questions/690039-i-need-a-book-in-which-john-calvin-said">I need a book in which John Calvin said: &quot; a dog barks when his master is attacked....?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_690039'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F232467.Institutes_of_the_Christian_Religion_2_Vols">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
