              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13333297623885500216">Hard to put into words how great this was. Each page is marked by reverence for God and His self-revealing Word, lucid thinking, courage, and a grasp of historical theology. A theological and devotional masterpiece.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


